						<summary>

						<p>On a stone built into the bastion in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1682, Vikrama, Kārtika, ba 2, Monday.</p>						

						<p>Records the construction of bastion <hi rend="italic">(buruzu)</hi> by a certain Rāmi-Reḍḍi, son of Timmāreḍḍi, during the regime of Rāja Śrī Bālaveṅkaṭa-Reḍḍi.</p>						

